videos.description: Braxton Key takes the pass in the corner and drives through traffic to knock down sweet layup.
videos.headline: Alabama's Key hits contested layup

videos.description: Collin Sexton pushes the ball down the court and uses a spin move to knock down a shot for the Tide.
videos.headline: Alabama's Sexton drives, spins and scores

videos.description: Nick Weatherspoon comes up with a loose ball and takes it to the rack to throw down a big slam for Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Weatherspoon goes coast-to-coast for huge dunk

videos.description: Off a steal, Alabama's Collin Sexton lobs a perfect pass for Donta Hall to throw down the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Sexton finds Hall for big alley-oop

videos.description: After an Aric Holman block sets up a fast break, Quinndary Weatherspoon throws down a two-handed slam off of the behind-the-back pass from Xavian Stapleton.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Holman's block sets up big Weatherspoon slam
